data.text: @Blondecalabrian I literally felt the pain. It wasn't much a secret for long time fans. But to actually hear her say it out loud. That was heart wrenching. @Mariska I just wanted to hug Benson.
@Blondecalabrian Amazing- mesmerizing scenes-old wounds- damn that was epic
@Blondecalabrian Certainly had a healthier respect for it after watching a second time.
